claim: Jeff Bezos is an American entrepreneur.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Jeff Bezos  (  -LSB- ˈbeɪzoʊs -RSB- born Jeffrey Preston Jorgensen ; January 12 , 1964  )  is an American technology and retail entrepreneur , investor , and philanthropist who is best known as the founder , chairman , and chief executive officer of Amazon.com , which is the world 's largest online shopping retailer .
